        Inclusion Criteria:

        Patients operated in Ain Shams University Hospitals for aortic and/ or mitral valve
        replacement.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Congenital blood disorders, Hemophilia.

          -  Advanced liver disease

          -  Advanced renal disease (dialysis patients)

          -  Aspirin sensitivity

          -  Autoimmune diseases

          -  Biological bioprosthesis valves

          -  Non-compliant &amp; Drop out patient

          -  Pregnant women

          -  Caucasians.
      </textblock>
